    "offset": 240732,
    "slot_size": 262,
    "data_size": 258,
    "nom_orig": "Eikichi",
    "texte_orig": "What's[SP]those[SP]two's[SP]problem!?[SP]I[SP]know[SP]it's[SP]the\nrumors[SP]warping[SP]their[SP]brains,[SP]but[SP]why[SP]do[SP]they\nhave[SP]to[SP]say[SP]it[SP]like[SP]that!?",
