    "texte_orig": "Thinking[SP]ahead,[SP]part[SP]2![SP]Never[SP]neglect[SP]defense\nwhen[SP]it[SP]comes[SP]to[SP]a[SP]fight.[SP]Always[SP]have[SP]the\nbest[SP]armor[SP]you[SP]can[SP]get[SP]your[SP]hands[SP]on.",
